properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 4 at 2:56PM EST until January 5 at 7:00AM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 6 to 9 feet expected.

* WHERE...Gulf waters from the Walton-Okaloosa County line to
the Suwannee river out 60 nautical miles.

* WHEN...Until 7 AM EST /6 AM CST/ Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 AM EST /6 AM CST/ SUNDAY
